WEBVTT

00:00:20.645 --> 00:00:21.521
(We're dating.)

00:00:25.108 --> 00:00:26.943
(We're in a relationship.)

00:00:31.573 --> 00:00:33.616
Were you feeling unwell this morning?

00:00:36.036 --> 00:00:36.619
Huh?

00:00:37.829 --> 00:00:38.913
What about Saebyeok?
[*"Morning" sounds similar to "Saebyeok" in Korean]

00:00:40.123 --> 00:00:40.749
Huh?

00:00:44.210 --> 00:00:45.879
I'm just asking if you felt unwell.

00:00:48.465 --> 00:00:49.591
Oh, you said morning.

00:00:50.133 --> 00:00:53.094
You're fine. Don't worry.

00:00:54.179 --> 00:00:56.306
(Dummy: Are you feeling okay?)
(Dummy: Photo)
(Dummy: Let's come here together)
Did you eat on time?

00:00:56.890 --> 00:00:59.851
you feel unwell,
please let me know at any time.

